#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "Compressing native executables using UPX"
msgstr "CompactaĂ§ĂŁo de executĂˇveis nativos com UPX"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid ""
"https://upx.github.io/[Ultimate Packer for eXecutables (UPX)] is a compression tool reducing the size of executables.\n"
"Quarkus can compress the produced native executable to reduce its size.\n"
"Such compression is interesting when:"
msgstr "O link:https://upx.github.io/[Ultimate Packer for eXecutables (UPX)] Ă© uma ferramenta de compactaĂ§ĂŁo que reduz o tamanho dos executĂˇveis. O Quarkus pode compactar o executĂˇvel nativo produzido para reduzir seu tamanho. Essa compactaĂ§ĂŁo Ă© interessante quando:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "building CLI tools, and you want to reduce the disk footprint,"
msgstr "Criando ferramentas CLI, e se vocĂŞ pretende reduzir o espaĂ§o ocupado pelo disco,"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "building small container images."
msgstr "construir pequenas imagens de containers."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "Note that UPX compression:"
msgstr "Note que a compactaĂ§ĂŁo UPX:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "increases your build time, mainly if you use high-compression levels"
msgstr "aumenta o tempo de build, principalmente se vocĂŞ utilizar nĂ­veis de compactaĂ§ĂŁo elevados"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "increases the startup RSS usage of the application"
msgstr "aumenta a utilizaĂ§ĂŁo do RSS de startup da aplicaĂ§ĂŁo"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "System vs. Container"
msgstr "Sistema vs. Container"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "The UPX compression requires:"
msgstr "A compressĂŁo UPX requer:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "the `upx` command to be available in the system `PATH`;"
msgstr "o comando `upx` deve estar disponĂ­vel no `PATH`;"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "an explicitly defined `quarkus.native.compression.container-image`;"
msgstr "um `quarkus.native.compression.container-image` definido explicitamente;"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "or to have built the native executable using an in-container build."
msgstr "ou ter construĂ­do o executĂˇvel nativo usando uma compilaĂ§ĂŁo dentro de um container."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If `quarkus.native.compression.container-image` is not set explicitly, it will implicitly default to `quarkus.native.builder-image`."
msgstr "Se `quarkus.native.compression.container-image` nĂŁo for definido explicitamente, o padrĂŁo implĂ­cito serĂˇ `quarkus.native.builder-image` ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you have the `upx` command available on your path, Quarkus uses it.\n"
"Otherwise, if you built the native image using an in-container build (using `quarkus.native.container-build=true`) and if the compression image provides the `upx` command, Quarkus compresses the executable from inside the container."
msgstr "Se o senhor tiver o comando `upx` disponĂ­vel no caminho, o Quarkus o utilizarĂˇ. Caso contrĂˇrio, se o senhor construiu a imagem nativa usando uma construĂ§ĂŁo dentro do contĂŞiner (usando `quarkus.native.container-build=true` ) e se a imagem de compactaĂ§ĂŁo fornecer o comando `upx` , o Quarkus compacta o executĂˇvel de dentro do contĂŞiner."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you want to force compression to take place in a container, you can set `quarkus.native.compression.container-build` to `true` (or `false` to explicitly not run compression in a container)."
msgstr "Se quiser forĂ§ar a compactaĂ§ĂŁo a ocorrer em um contĂŞiner, defina `quarkus.native.compression.container-build` como `true` (ou `false` para nĂŁo executar explicitamente a compactaĂ§ĂŁo em um contĂŞiner)."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "If you are not in one of these cases, the compression fails."
msgstr "Se vocĂŞ nĂŁo estiver em num destes casos, a compactaĂ§ĂŁo falha."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Setting `quarkus.native.compression.container-image` results in the compression to run in a container.\n"
"If you want to set the variable, but not run the compression in a container, set `quarkus.native.compression.container-build` explicitly to `false`."
msgstr "A definiĂ§ĂŁo de `quarkus.native.compression.container-image` faz com que a compactaĂ§ĂŁo seja executada em um contĂŞiner. Se quiser definir a variĂˇvel, mas nĂŁo executar a compactaĂ§ĂŁo em um contĂŞiner, defina `quarkus.native.compression.container-build` explicitamente como `false` ."

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`WORKDIR` for the image used for compression"
msgstr "`WORKDIR` para a imagem usada para compressĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The executable to compress is mounted in directory `/project`.\n"
"Since the container runs `upx` in the current working directory, the `WORKDIR` of the image used for compression must be `/project`."
msgstr "O executĂˇvel a ser compactado Ă© montado no diretĂłrio `/project` . Como o contĂŞiner executa `o upx` no diretĂłrio de trabalho atual, o `WORKDIR` da imagem usada para compactaĂ§ĂŁo deve ser `/project` ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Compression can be explicitly en-/disabled by setting `quarkus.native.compression.enabled`."
msgstr "A compactaĂ§ĂŁo pode ser explicitamente ativada/desativada com a configuraĂ§ĂŁo `quarkus.native.compression.enabled` ."

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "upx is cross-platform."
msgstr "O upx Ă© multiplataforma."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "`upx` can compress executables using a different architecture and OS than your host machine. For example, `upx` on a macOS machine can compress a Linux 64-bits executables."
msgstr "`upx` pode comprimir executĂˇveis utilizando uma arquitetura e um sistema operacional diferentes dos da sua mĂˇquina anfitriĂŁ. Por exemplo, `upx` numa mĂˇquina macOS pode compactar um executĂˇvel Linux de 64 bits."

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "Configuring the UPX compression"
msgstr "ConfiguraĂ§ĂŁo da compactaĂ§ĂŁo UPX"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "Then, in your application configuration, enable the compression by configuring the _compression level_ you want:"
msgstr "Em seguida, na configuraĂ§ĂŁo da aplicaĂ§ĂŁo, ative a compactaĂ§ĂŁo, configurando o _nĂ­vel de compactaĂ§ĂŁo_ pretendido:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid ""
"If the compression level is not set, the compression is disabled.\n"
"The compression will happen once the native executable is built and will replace the executable."
msgstr "Se o nĂ­vel de compactaĂ§ĂŁo nĂŁo for definido, a compactaĂ§ĂŁo serĂˇ desativada. A compactaĂ§ĂŁo ocorrerĂˇ quando o executĂˇvel nativo for criado e substituirĂˇ o executĂˇvel."

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "Compression level"
msgstr "NĂ­vel de compactaĂ§ĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "The compression level goes from 1 to 10:"
msgstr "O nĂ­vel de compactaĂ§ĂŁo vai de 1 a 10:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "`1`: faster compression"
msgstr "`1`: compactaĂ§ĂŁo mais rĂˇpida"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "`9`: better compression"
msgstr "`9`: melhor compactaĂ§ĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/upx.adoc
msgid "`10`: best compression (can be slow for big files)"
msgstr "`10`: melhor compactaĂ§ĂŁo (pode ser lenta para pastas grandes)"

